HEADWORD: Gildale
<hw>Gild"ale`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[AS.
<ets>gilgan</ets> to pay + E. <ets>ale</ets>. See <er>Yield</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos>, and <er>Ale</er>.]</ety> <def>A drinking bout in which
every one pays an equal share.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

